docstring.short_description: Multiply two numeric arrays, vectors, matrices, or constants element-wise.

parameters.name: a
parameters.description: The input a use to compute the product of a and b.

parameters.name: b
parameters.description: The input b use to compute the product of a and b.

returns.description:
OrderedPair if a is an OrderedPair.
x: the x-axis of input a.
y: the result of the product of input a and input b.

Scalar if a is a Scalar.
c: the result of the product of input a and input b.

Vector if a is a Vector.
v: the result of the product of input a and input b.
